{"tid":583902,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"手術後膊頭好痛","createTime":"2018-03-07T11:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T12:09:16.000Z","uid":13268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58e5920d76a089b21252bc49ea78230000624f2c","tid":583902,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"老婆尋日做完婦科手術<br />\n係做傳統開腹手術，唔係微創手術<br />\n尋日可能藥物關係佢唔覺得痛<br />\n今日藥力過後佢膊頭痛到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊到要搵護士醫生黎睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫生話因為手術後仲有氣體留在體內<br />\n氣體上升到佢膊頭位令佢有痛感<br />\n下午食左止痛藥都仲痛..<br />\n訓唔到落床休息唔到<br />\n已經幫佢按摩左好耐，按完過一陣又痛<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咩好方法幫佢舒緩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話仲要等一兩日先會自然好，但唔忍心見到佢依家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f92b49535b02e0521681b22fc7e9dfac3673932","tid":583902,"uid":125703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"我試過，做婦科微創全身麻醉。做完膊頭痛到顛左，轉都轉唔到身。大約3~4日倒慢慢好d, 然後就完全無事。醫生話係麻醉藥問題，會散"},{"pid":"fec7c00023192ed47084051c5a5c7d9006d8b1c7","tid":583902,"uid":125703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"補充多句，無野紓媛到，痛幾日自然會好"},{"pid":"7348da6d4f6ab3d1bf4b52409b2258753491980d","tid":583902,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"醫生咪話自然會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}